name: Jessie Wong
about: Hi, I'm Jessie. I am a sophomore majoring in Computer Science. Aside from DTI, I am also involved in WICC, CTAS, and OASIS. I'm passionate about improving the communities around me, making meaningful connections with others, and achieving financial independence. You can find me on campus curating playlists, jamming out to musicals, and getting takeout at SoPoong :D. Feel free to chat me up if any of this stuff seems of interest to you!
